      "short": "",
      "unidentified": "",
      "value": "<p>&gt;@UUID[Compendium.sfrpg.class-features.Item.XrBOn1MueVB4u5sV]{Nanocyte Knack}</p>\n<p>Your nanites infest a nearby corpse, animating it as a combatant. You can spend a @UUID[Compendium.sfrpg.class-features.Item.vh6n0Ad3lamOJXpV]{Nanite Surge (Ex)} as a standard action to turn one or more corpses into a number of @UUID[Compendium.sfrpg.alien-archives.Item.Lm6T2ReFaBXLoXbB]{Cybernetic Zombies}<sup>AA</sup> with a total CR of no more than half your nanocyte level. A zombie can be created only from a creature with a physical anatomy. These zombies can do nothing but attack your enemies nearest to them, and they last a number of rounds equal to your Constitution modifier.</p>"
